Apakah ini?

526
00:33:35,667 --> 00:33:37,333
Apa yang berlaku?

527
00:33:49,946 --> 00:33:52,090
[Pengintipan, Jenayah, Bencana,
Pusat Pelaporan]

528
00:35:00,133 --> 00:35:01,733
awak punk!

529
