Saya kehilangan dia kerana awak!

552
00:36:12,067 --> 00:36:13,800
Kehilangan dia?

553
00:36:15,642 --> 00:36:16,933
sial!

554
00:36:16,933 --> 00:36:18,533
Bagaimana anda boleh kehilangan dia?

555
00:36:18,533 --> 00:36:21,033
Detektif Do, saya beritahu awak!

556
00:36:21,033 --> 00:36:22,167
Kita tak mampu kehilangan dia.

557
00:36:22,167 --> 00:36:25,067
Saya minta maaf, tuan.

558
00:36:25,067 --> 00:36:26,800
Apa tunggu lagi Kejar dia.

559
00:36:26,800 --> 00:36:28,633
Ya, tuan.

560
00:36:31,133 --> 00:36:32,600
Adakah anda?

561
00:36:32,600 --> 00:36:35,267
Yang tarik pegawai balai kita ke sini?

562
00:36:35,267 --> 00:36:36,733
Adakah anda mempunyai sebarang idea
apa yang kita sedang usahakan sekarang?

563
00:36:36,733 --> 00:36:40,733
Ini sama seriusnya
sebagai pembunuhan bersiri.

564
00:36:40,733 --> 00:36:43,467
Ini soal keselamatan negara!

565
00:36:44,733 --> 00:36:46,304
Jangan sekali-kali

566
00:36:46,304 --> 00:36:48,733
seret detektif kami ke dalam perkara ini lagi.

567
00:36:50,533 --> 00:36:52,167
Detektif Kang.

568
00:36:52,867 --> 00:36:55,167
Awak terus lupa.

569
00:36:55,167 --> 00:36:56,933
Saya pendakwa

570
00:36:56,933 --> 00:36:59,067
